Abuja ( Sundiata Post) – The vocal Nigerian senator, Dino Melaye who has been rumored by many to be in the race to contest for the governorship seat in Kogi State, has officially declared himself as an aspirant. Senator Dino Melaye has been of the frontline critics of the Yahaya Bello led administration in Kogi State and his declaration to contest against the incumbent comes as no surprise to many. The senator was returned elected as Senator respenting the people of Kogi central during the 2019 election. The governorship election in Kogi State is scheduled to hold in November 2019. See post below: The post Breaking: Dino Melaye Officially Enters Kogi Governorship Race appeared first on Information Nigeria. Visit website